      "column": "left",
      "text": "Atkat mehroja wiꞥſch tuhſtoſchas Ohlektis/ un wiꞥſch lihke manni zaur Uhdent pahreet/\nun tas Uhdens freedsahs man lihds Zetteem/ un wiꞥſch mehroja wehl tuhſtoſchas Ohlektis/ un tas Uhdens freedsahs man lihds Gurneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Atkat mehroja Wiꞥſch tuhſtoſchas Ohlektis/ tad bija Uppe/ kur es ne warreju zaureet/\njo tas Uhdens bija dſitſch/ tahds Uhdens/zaur ko bij japeld/weena Uppe/ kur ne warreja zaureet.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch fazzija us man:\nEſſi tu to redsejs tu Zilweka Behrns? tad wedde Wiꞥſchmann/ un atwedde mann atkat Uppes Mallā.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rad es nu atgreeſohs/rangi/ tad bija pee tahs Uppes Malias tohti dauds Kohlu/ no schihs un no winnas Puﬀes.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fazzija wiꞥſch us man: Schis Uhdens istek prett Galilejas Nihta Puﬀi/ un notek Klaijuma/ pehz to nahk tae Juhrā/ un no Juhras istezzejs/tape tas Uhdens weffeligs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas notiks/ ka wiffada dſihwa Dwafcha/ kas kuſtahs wiﬀur/ korp jebkahda no tahm diwi Uppehm nahk/dſihwohs/ un tur buhs fohti dauds Siwju/ tapehz ka schis Uhdens turp nahks/ un tee taps weffeli/un dſihwohs wiﬀur/ kur schi Uppe tiks.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir Sweineeki pee tahsim/ kas starp Damaskuta Roh-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tomehr winnas Paltis un winnas Purwij ne taps wefſeligi/ tee taps par Sahlu darriti.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un pee tahs Uppes usaugē pee winnas Mallas abbejās Puﬀēs wiſſadi angligt Kohki/ kurru Lappas ne nobirs/neds tee Augki mittefees/ un neſtihs ſawōs Mehneſchōs jaunus Augtus. Jo winnas Uhdens iſtek no tahs ſwehtas Weetas / un winnas Auglis buhs par Barribu/un winnas Lappas par Dseedinaſchanu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta takka tas Kungs KI-NGS: Schi laid irr ta Rohbescha / pehz kurras juws to Semmi par Eemantofchanu buhs nemt/ pehz tahm diwipadefnits Israēta Ziltim/ Jahsepam peenahk diwi Dattas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un jums buhs to eeman-toht/ weens tik labbi ka obtrs/pahr ko es fawn Rohku efmu pazehlis/ ka es to juhtu Tehweem dohtu / un fcht Semme jums peekrittibs par Eemantofchanu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Schi nu irr ta Semmes Rohbescha prett Seemeta-Puffi/ no leelas Juhras/ tas Zetsch no Etiona / kur us Jedadu nahk.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Eemats/ Verots/Sibra-\n"
    }
  ],
